{"tid":659334,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[無式] [細電] 講下數位電路點運作","createTime":"2018-05-09T17:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T15:58:40.000Z","uid":147721,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7eca1aaeaf63d14df694c1c2f1778d7430d13530","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"講下廢話先 reply先開波<br />\n<br />\n開呢個PO係因為睇到&quot;CPU物理運作原理之疑問&quot;呢個PO 但係已經變左做半個私怨PO 所以先開新PO講而唔係個個PO回<br />\n我無睇晒個個PO 所以講既野可能同其他巴打講過既野重複<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我講既野既角度 係簡易同初步既computer architecture<br />\n所以當我講電晶體/電路設計個時 我唔會亦無能力講得好精準好深入 只會講概念 細節部分好可能係會有錯<br />\n歡迎各位巴打補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係唔好屌我講漏野/唔講某啲野 因為我真係預先係到事先講明我講唔到啲細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f32fa489a39b5cebf69b5229483e96a4193793","tid":659334,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:21:39.000Z","msg":"lm學野"},{"pid":"5c5243e11d6558331f7e804446ea86b263ef3917","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:22:12.000Z","msg":"相信大家係科學館見過一個展品 係開閂燈制去科普logic gate<br />\n相信IQ180既連登仔都有以下諗法<br />\n1. 鬼唔知如果同一條電線有兩個制既話 要兩個制都close先可以着燈咩<br />\n2. 鬼唔知如果parallel有兩個制既話 求其一個制close就已經可以着燈咩<br />\n3. 屌 CPU入面撚有制呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講完都唔撚知電晶體點運作既<br />\n咁到底電晶體係點構成數位電路呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電晶體有好多種既 我就揀FET黎講(MOSFET) 唔講BJT了 因為我覺得講FET會易啲理解個電路<br />\n<br />\n先非常簡單咁講一個FET既結構 (其實FET仲有好多細分既 我呢個係舉例<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/004941_a8a26b6d9dee78ad3efaced6c5c5fbb5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F004941_a8a26b6d9dee78ad3efaced6c5c5fbb5.png&h=b53924bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFET有三個極 <span style=\"color: red;\">gate</span>係用黎控制通過<span style=\"color: red;\">source</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">drain</span>既電流 <br />\n呢個係一個n型FET source同drain都係n type半導體 即係佢地係有好多電子既<br />\nbody就係p type半導體 係超級少電子同有好多電洞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係呢個狀態下 source同drain之間係唔會有電流既 因為電流只可以由p流去n 唔可以由n流去p 而source-body-drain之間係npn既結構 電流通過唔到當中既np 而上面舊oxide係絕緣體 更加通唔到電<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果我地係gate到施加一個正電壓既話 body既電子(好少但係有 而且視電路設計 body係可以接個電極去係外部獲得電子)就會被吸引過去近gate既地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/004942_df0f6a79d96a0d3a312076b3be9742c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F004942_df0f6a79d96a0d3a312076b3be9742c9.png&h=4bb700e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當gate既電壓大到一定程度 近gate既地方就會變做少電洞多電子 即係變做同n type半導體差唔多既狀態<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/004943_f7ecabb2d37ce29eb41bf4ad53ab0147.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F004943_f7ecabb2d37ce29eb41bf4ad53ab0147.png&h=ad35b7e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係呢個狀態之下 source-body-drain之間就有一個nnn既結構 呢個結構係通到電既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小結: FET令我地可以用gate既電壓 去控制source-drain之間通唔通到電<br />\n(頭盔: 其實仲有好多細節值得研究 例如source-drain既IV關係 漏電流 等等等等 我就唔深入講了 等其他巴打補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n但係有個問題: FET既輸入既電壓 但係輸出係通電/唔通電 輸入既&quot;格式&quot;同輸出既&quot;格式&quot;都唔同 到底CPU入面啲電晶體係點樣一層接住一層咁傳遞訊號呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個問題陣間會講 而家我去趕尾班小巴返屋企先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bdb48381850e3f8f1ed37e5fa5aa2655e6e58f","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:30:23.000Z","msg":"補link<br />\nCPU物理運作原理之疑問<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/658178/page/7?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/658178/page/7?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c77679f87ffd2954f4b8c9fb7fac54a8057673d5","tid":659334,"uid":41355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:31:49.000Z","msg":"留名支持復興學術台"},{"pid":"50adb238e0c6a6e79e09fee7b7beca29ded7aece","tid":659334,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<br />\n利申:讀過"},{"pid":"22870a3d93a59397fff40df5a7090914688fa9b9","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50adb238e0c6a6e79e09fee7b7beca29ded7aece","tid":659334,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<br />\n利申:讀過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係讀ee 所以有錯屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ded5ffce9112631e1f4405b5ac5f444fc06ac2","tid":659334,"uid":22394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0b360b0bbabe35b14c95ae6fd3fe938a6625052a","tid":659334,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22870a3d93a59397fff40df5a7090914688fa9b9","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50adb238e0c6a6e79e09fee7b7beca29ded7aece","tid":659334,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<br />\n利申:讀過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係讀ee 所以有錯屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:37:21.000Z","msg":"唔緊要<br />\nbtw我覺得講基本原理就得, 唔洗咁詳細<br />\nFET用 開關 做例子就夠<br />\ndetail 野 讀書/自己睇書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f97e474455a0afd7c60de848c7c7c2f6b36b30","tid":659334,"uid":34530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"支持高汁，十幾年前讀過，已忘記唒"},{"pid":"51046ed51b5c002909879bb12f0e703c30e25f2c","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:50:27.000Z","msg":"上到小巴了 繼續講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地由電晶體結構移上一層 講電路了<br />\n頭盔: 我用既電路完全無做任何optimization 現實上應該唔會係咁簡單 尤其係我個電路功耗會好大<br />\n幾廿年前先會用咁既電路 好似係<br />\n<br />\n如果想用一個電晶體去控制燈膽着唔着 連登仔第一下可能會咁：(Vdd係電路操作電壓<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/013938_b956aa2704e1235b7b61a1361f086967.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F013938_b956aa2704e1235b7b61a1361f086967.png&h=bef75da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但咁有個問題<br />\nVdd一般同燈膽既操作電壓唔同 如果Vdd太細燈膽就唔着 Vdd太大電晶體就會燒<br />\n<br />\n所以正確做法會係咁（呢個電路順便講埋點做A and B<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/014247_f02f813865750f368108595c79e74cd3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F014247_f02f813865750f368108595c79e74cd3.png&h=335d58cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係A B電晶體到 我地係下方再接多個電阻 同時拉一條線出黎作為A and B既output<br />\n當A同B都係正電壓個時 上半part就會係通電=好低電阻 而下半part係我地放既大電阻 所以output線既電壓就會係Vdd<br />\n相反 如果A或者B有一個係ground個時 上半part就會係斷電 雖然下半part係大電阻 但上半part斷電 所以output線既電壓就會係ground了<br />\n透過拉電阻去ground既手法 我地將個輸出既格式由通/斷電 改做高/低電壓<br />\n呢個輸出電壓我地再拎去做另一個特殊電晶體既輸入 呢個特殊電晶體係可以承受大電壓電流既 可以同個電膽一齊操作 咁就可以開關燈膽了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb219b13a9cdeaf3ca2b84e5a7ee45c46283332","tid":659334,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51046ed51b5c002909879bb12f0e703c30e25f2c","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:50:27.000Z","msg":"上到小巴了 繼續講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地由電晶體結構移上一層 講電路了<br />\n頭盔: 我用既電路完全無做任何optimization 現實上應該唔會係咁簡單 尤其係我個電路功耗會好大<br />\n幾廿年前先會用咁既電路 好似係<br />\n<br />\n如果想用一個電晶體去控制燈膽着唔着 連登仔第一下可能會咁：(Vdd係電路操作電壓<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/013938_b956aa2704e1235b7b61a1361f086967.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F013938_b956aa2704e1235b7b61a1361f086967.png&h=bef75da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但咁有個問題<br />\nVdd一般同燈膽既操作電壓唔同 如果Vdd太細燈膽就唔着 Vdd太大電晶體就會燒<br />\n<br />\n所以正確做法會係咁（呢個電路順便講埋點做A and B<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/014247_f02f813865750f368108595c79e74cd3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F014247_f02f813865750f368108595c79e74cd3.png&h=335d58cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係A B電晶體到 我地係下方再接多個電阻 同時拉一條線出黎作為A and B既output<br />\n當A同B都係正電壓個時 上半part就會係通電=好低電阻 而下半part係我地放既大電阻 所以output線既電壓就會係Vdd<br />\n相反 如果A或者B有一個係ground個時 上半part就會係斷電 雖然下半part係大電阻 但上半part斷電 所以output線既電壓就會係ground了<br />\n透過拉電阻去ground既手法 我地將個輸出既格式由通/斷電 改做高/低電壓<br />\n呢個輸出電壓我地再拎去做另一個特殊電晶體既輸入 呢個特殊電晶體係可以承受大電壓電流既 可以同個電膽一齊操作 咁就可以開關燈膽了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:57:57.000Z","msg":"想講CMOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7db4d