.000Z","msg":"想講CMOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:02:54.000Z","msg":"唔了 等你補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然低功耗 但係覺得講下電阻手法會好啲 因為我可以偷懶唔駛講p type FET<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:04:44.000Z","msg":"當開關就係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nn / p type 可以唔多講, 提一提就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fecab35aeb48dc52335132e0854aff561aa4e40","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7db4d50738e1171fdd6af68e59a9d8c4b1d15a9","tid":659334,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceb219b13a9cdeaf3ca2b84e5a7ee45c46283332","tid":659334,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51046ed51b5c002909879bb12f0e703c30e25f2c","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:50:27.000Z","msg":"上到小巴了 繼續講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地由電晶體結構移上一層 講電路了<br />\n頭盔: 我用既電路完全無做任何optimization 現實上應該唔會係咁簡單 尤其係我個電路功耗會好大<br />\n幾廿年前先會用咁既電路 好似係<br />\n<br />\n如果想用一個電晶體去控制燈膽着唔着 連登仔第一下可能會咁：(Vdd係電路操作電壓<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/013938_b956aa2704e1235b7b61a1361f086967.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F013938_b956aa2704e1235b7b61a1361f086967.png&h=bef75da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但咁有個問題<br />\nVdd一般同燈膽既操作電壓唔同 如果Vdd太細燈膽就唔着 Vdd太大電晶體就會燒<br />\n<br />\n所以正確做法會係咁（呢個電路順便講埋點做A and B<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/014247_f02f813865750f368108595c79e74cd3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F014247_f02f813865750f368108595c79e74cd3.png&h=335d58cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係A B電晶體到 我地係下方再接多個電阻 同時拉一條線出黎作為A and B既output<br />\n當A同B都係正電壓個時 上半part就會係通電=好低電阻 而下半part係我地放既大電阻 所以output線既電壓就會係Vdd<br />\n相反 如果A或者B有一個係ground個時 上半part就會係斷電 雖然下半part係大電阻 但上半part斷電 所以output線既電壓就會係ground了<br />\n透過拉電阻去ground既手法 我地將個輸出既格式由通/斷電 改做高/低電壓<br />\n呢個輸出電壓我地再拎去做另一個特殊電晶體既輸入 呢個特殊電晶體係可以承受大電壓電流既 可以同個電膽一齊操作 咁就可以開關燈膽了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:57:57.000Z","msg":"想講CMOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:02:48.000Z","msg":"你似講緊pull-down, 如果講digital circuit, 多數會講cmos 點做not gate 或者 and gate"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"Yes就係講緊pull down<br />\n講埋CMOS電路都可以既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過要講埋p type FET先"},{"pid":"7e82d2594d35dc8cd553387c1806ccb9417ee942","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b360b0bbabe35b14c95ae6fd3fe938a6625052a","tid":659334,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22870a3d93a59397fff40df5a7090914688fa9b9","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50adb238e0c6a6e79e09fee7b7beca29ded7aece","tid":659334,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<br />\n利申:讀過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係讀ee 所以有錯屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:37:21.000Z","msg":"唔緊要<br />\nbtw我覺得講基本原理就得, 唔洗咁詳細<br />\nFET用 開關 做例子就夠<br />\ndetail 野 讀書/自己睇書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:07:15.000Z","msg":"唔想就咁講開關 因為其實好多人都明開關點form logic gate 佢地最唔明既係電晶體點做開關 同埋通/斷電既格式點變做電壓格式"},{"pid":"f5aa5b52e98c4f91d38a2a87493ba40833b9edbc","tid":659334,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:15:56.000Z","msg":"樓主可唔可以講吓mosfet cmos運作原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2年前take microelectronic device讀到1 pat屎,去見工畀人問到口啞啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bc3ae798a3131b5ccac13fb8f9d3dec31c30c4","tid":659334,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:17:35.000Z","msg":"留名嘗試理解下"},{"pid":"6484ba70ae61f2f503dcd08646984fd4b6876131","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:19:35.000Z","msg":"講左and既circuit 講埋or既circuit了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/021648_0385b30e731848dad2f4fef124282b78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F021648_0385b30e731848dad2f4fef124282b78.png&h=faaadb1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同科學館講既一樣 series咁駁係and parallel咁駁係or<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n複雜啲既例子 (A and B) or C<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/021810_e10f56133bba088575955a8ab5f6fa94.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F021810_e10f56133bba088575955a8ab5f6fa94.png&h=6cfb7f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然啦 其實有更有效率既駁法 但係我主要係想show下啲訊號點樣一層層咁傳遞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日講到呢到 聽日返到office先再畫圖講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8ecd3aa37e79e32e68b2520bfeb6d4e3e313ea","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5aa5b52e98c4f91d38a2a87493ba40833b9edbc","tid":659334,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:15:56.000Z","msg":"樓主可唔可以講吓mosfet cmos運作原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2年前take microelectronic device讀到1 pat屎,去見工畀人問到口啞啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"Ching我講唔到教科書答案比你聽 因為我唔係讀ee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面十年巴提到左CMOS 我之後會嘗試講下既 但真心一定會有野講漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好有期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11d65f224e1a7b7964434c890e9af2d77ed9331","tid":659334,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e82d2594d35dc8cd553387c1806ccb9417ee942","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b360b0bbabe35b14c95ae6fd3fe938a6625052a","tid":659334,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22870a3d93a59397fff40df5a7090914688fa9b9","tid":659334,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係讀ee 所以有錯屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:37:21.000Z","msg":"唔緊要<br />\nbtw我覺得講基本原理就得, 唔洗咁詳細<br />\nFET用 開關 做例子就夠<br />\ndetail 野 讀書/自己睇書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:07:15.000Z","msg":"唔想就咁講開關 因為其實好多人都明開關點form logic gate 佢地最唔明既係電晶體點做開關 同埋通/斷電既格式點變做電壓格式"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T00:31:37.000Z","msg"